        "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:12:2",
        "relations": null,
        "text": [
          " أَصْحَابُ الْكَبَائِرِ كُلِّهَا إِذَا أُقِيمَ عَلَيْهِمُ الْحَدُّ مَرَّتَيْنِ قُتِلُوا فِي الثَّالِثَةِ ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.hubeali": [
            "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Safwan, from Yunus, ",
            "(It has been narrated) from Abu Al Hassan ‘Al-Maazy’ (the 7<sup>th</sup> Imam<sup>asws</sup>) having said: ‘The committers of the major sins, all of them, when the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) is established twice upon them, they would be killed (after) the third’."
          ]
        }
      }
